  "prompt": "Can I download and listen to music in offline mode on the Spotify app on Volvo Sensus?",
  "response": "As of my last update, the Spotify app on the Volvo Sensus infotainment system does not support offline listening. The app allows you to stream music directly from Spotify, but it requires an active internet connection via cellular data or a Wi-Fi hotspot to do so. Offline listening typically requires downloading tracks to a device and playing them without an internet connection, a feature available on mobile devices with Spotify Premium but not directly supported on the Volvo Sensus system.\n\nFor the most accurate information, you might want to check the latest updates from Spotify or Volvo, as features and capabilities can change with new software updates.",
